  <brief_title>Platelet Aggregation Inhibition in Children on Clopidogrel (PICOLO)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dose-Ranging Pharmacodynamic Assessment of Platelet Aggregation Inhibition With Clopidogrel in Children of Blalock-Taussig Shunt Age Categories (Neonates and Infants/Toddlers)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
